# Choose the correct tense

1. My mother (make/**makes**) delicious cakes.
2. The Sun (rise/**rises**) in the East.
3. She (listening/**is listening**) to the news.
4. He (distribute/**distributes**) newspapers. 
5. Kamal (feed/**feeds**) the stray dogs.
6. John (wait/**waited**) for the train to arrive.
7. Ravi (**is working**/work) at the super market.
8. The children (take/**took**) the sweets from the shelf.
9. We (watch/**watched**) the solar eclipse last week.
10. Charu (**will give**/gave) a dance performance today evening.
